                        "displayName": "Weston Pace",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
                    },
                    "body": "A semaphore will allow me to control how many files I'm writing to at once but not how many files I have open (whether I am writing to them or not).  I need to close the old files so that the file handle is returned to the OS.  That means closing the writer and starting a new file later if more data comes in for that file.",
