                        },
                        "displayName": "Antoine Pitrou",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Paris"
                    },
                    "body": "You would acquire the semaphore when opening a file and release it when closing the file. I'm not sure I understand your use case?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
